{"tid":401241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歡送總監午宴位位400元惹不滿　通訊辦：純屬員工自願參加","createTime":"2017-09-15T12:34:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T16:13:50.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f95e9434a0ec8a8596c4fd4dbb0d684986952026","tid":401241,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:34:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">歡送總監午宴位位400元惹不滿　通訊辦：純屬員工自願參加</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170915/s00001/33e3e1e6db60e9bb47fffb763a60f5bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170915%2Fs00001%2F33e3e1e6db60e9bb47fffb763a60f5bb.jpg&h=e9240199&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本報收到投訴，指原通訊事務總監利敏貞出任商務及經濟發展局常任秘書長，辦公室為了歡送她，今日中午在灣仔一間酒樓包廂食飯，出席同事位位要付400元。有同事質疑午餐也要如此消費而有微言，但稱上頭要他們定必科水兼出席，甚表無奈。記者今午在包廂外問了幾位出席者，但他們都說沒有這意見。通訊辦亦表示午宴純屬自願參加，強制出席之說屬失實指控。<br />\n<br />\n政府上月公布高層官員任命，當中通訊事務總監利敏貞出任商務及經濟發展局常任秘書長，接替退休的何淑兒；通訊事務總監一職由運輸及房屋局副秘書長王天予接任。<br />\n<br />\n為了歡送利敏貞，今日通訊事務管理局辦公室包廂午宴，記者中午前往陶源酒家，發現其中一間房外貼有「利小姐」的名牌。根據房外的菜單顯示，包廂內有4席，每席要3,980元，若連加一服務費等，每位平均要負責約400元也差不多。<br />\n<br />\n通訊事務管理局辦公室回應本報查詢時表示，今天中午通訊辦於灣仔酒樓所舉行的午宴，是為前通訊事務總監利敏貞所安排的歡送會，利女士是應通訊辦同事的邀請出席午宴，是次午宴純屬員工自願參加及付費的私人聚會。對於有指該聚會是強制性參加，是毫無事實根據及失實的指控。商經局則表示，利敏貞與通訊辦同事共事7年，今日她是應同事邀請出席歡送午宴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170915/s00001/1505473305465\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170915%2Fs00001%2F1505473305465&d=r8wrifD8mPE8JW4%2FQmjtOv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=dfab738b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170915%2Fs00001%2F1505473305465&h=3deffd57\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170915/s00001/1505473305465</a>"},{"pid":"e268d9405e23ca2fb0d472812a8bfc19a49e1956","tid":401241,"uid":73613,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:35:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"116fa7a4179dfcc2b9b4fc22bc73e3874b354773","tid":401241,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:39:54.000Z","msg":"話說柳記學堂阿一上星期五退休好似收得仲貴&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"363b858a034b30613cd77504fd3706c66ea8d8d1","tid":401241,"uid":17103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:41:04.000Z","msg":"謝師宴"},{"pid":"fa068e66932862e925727e6452550b019fdf594d","tid":401241,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:42:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班公務員奴隸格到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n公開反抗又唔敢，背後就屌鳩老細，但$400就死死地氣照比，荒死無左份工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7684762ea87b53b5d3685e715a6699f12d648055","tid":401241,"uid":43809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:43:03.000Z","msg":"黑色喱士利敏貞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1632508b18c0adfaa0059779f9462238848190d2","tid":401241,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:47:33.000Z","msg":"利敏貞當年唔俾wiki用流動牌開台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢副咀臉一世都記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a7820198d80c4fe448be840ac3170bdf65e427","tid":401241,"uid":50663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:49:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利敏貞當年唔俾wiki用流動牌開台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢副咀臉一世都記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n事實證明佢都唔算錯得哂"},{"pid":"337be89b103b3e3f3da01f19df95cc63a1a87787","tid":401241,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:55:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"318128900bca3fc0523497cf3cade759031248ce","t